      <p class="section-label">Social Mission</p>
      <h2 class="section-title" style="margin-bottom:2rem;">Law in service<br>of the <em>community</em></h2>
      <p>The philosophy of Tesserae undoubtedly has a social function, oriented toward providing volunteer legal services related to social rights, labor rights, human rights, and the protection of women and their inclusion in male-dominated sectors such as strategic infrastructure and construction.</p>
      <p>The team has directed many of its efforts to providing legal assistance to vulnerable women and their families, in transversal aspects that improve their quality of life.</p>
      <p><em>"The vision of doing justice binds us indubitably to a humanist and moral sense, which seeks to combine the professional strengths of our team in favor of society's most fragile and exposed segment — women."</em></p>
      <p>We also provide legal support to the <strong>Tesserae InfraLab Foundation</strong> (<a href="https://www.tesseraeinfralab.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color:var(--gold);">www.tesseraeinfralab.org</a>), whose goals include inclusion, employment, visibility, and gender-focused competency. The Foundation seeks to break the "glass ceiling" in male-dominated sectors.</p>
      <a href="/en/contact/" class="btn-primary" style="margin-top:2rem; display:inline-block;">Request Pro Bono Assistance</a>
    </div>

